### List all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Register a new customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullNames": "Jane Customer",
  "nationalId": "1199080012345678",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+250788111222",
  "address": "Kigali, Rwanda"
}

### Get a customer by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update a customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullNames": "Jane Customer Updated",
  "nationalId": "1199080012345678",
  "email": "jane.updated@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+250788111222",
  "address": "Kigali, Sector 3"
}

### Activate / deactivate a customer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}/status?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}